columns.name: ENTITY ROLE
columns.description: "General Contractor" or "Subcontractor"

columns.name: STREET ADDRESS
columns.description: The building/house number and street name, along with the suite/unit number (if applicable), on which the entity is located.

columns.name: CITY
columns.description: The city in which the entity is located.

columns.name: STATE
columns.description: The state in which the entity is located.

columns.name: POSTCODE
columns.description: The ZIP/postal code in which the entity is located.

columns.name: COUNTRY
columns.description: The country in which the entity is located.

columns.name: OWNER/OFFICER FIRST NAME
columns.description: The first name of an entity’s individual owner/officer. There may be multiple owners/officers listed for an entity.

columns.name: OWNER/OFFICER LAST NAME
columns.description: The last name of an entity’s individual owner/officer. There may be multiple owners/officers listed for an entity.

columns.name: Individual’s Role
columns.description: The role of the referenced individual within a sub-contractor (“Owner”, “Officer”, or “Both”).

columns.name: Individual’s Title
columns.description: The title given by the company to the referenced individual within the entity.

columns.name: Officer Equivalent
columns.description: The title equivalency of the title for an officer within an entity (“CEO”, “CFO”, “COO”, “NA”).

columns.name: BIN
columns.description: The Building Identification Number (BIN) associated with the provided entity location. It is formatted as a seven-digit numerical identifier, which is unique to each building in NYC.

columns.name: BBL
columns.description: The Borough, Block, Lot (BBL) associated with the provided entity location. It is formatted as a ten-digit numerical identifier, which is unique to each parcel of real property in NYC.

columns.name: COMMUNITY BOARD
columns.description: The NYC community board associated with the provided entity location (numbered 1 – 59, preceded by the borough code).

columns.name: COUNCIL DISTRICT
columns.description: The NYC council district associated with the provided entity location (numbered 1 – 51).

columns.name: CENSUS TRACT
columns.description: The US census tract associated with the provided entity location (in the format of up to four-digit integers, followed by an optional two-digit suffix e.g., “15.02” or “319”).

columns.name: NTA
columns.description: The Neighborhood Tabulation Area (NTA) associated with the provided entity location, which is formatted as a two-letter borough identifier followed by a two-digit numerical identifier (e.g., “BX31”).

columns.name: LATITUDE
columns.description: The latitude associated with the provided entity location.

columns.name: LONGITUDE
columns.description: The longitude associated with the provided entity location.
